{"sn11.21:0.1":"Samyutta Nikaya 11.21 ","sn11.21:0.2":"3. Tatiyavagga ","sn11.21:0.3":"Chetvasutta ","sn11.21:1.1":"Savatthiyam jetavane. ","sn11.21:1.2":"Atha kho sakko devanamindo yena bhagava tenupasankami; upasankamitva bhagavantam abhivadetva ekamantam atthasi. ","sn11.21:1.3":"Ekamantam thito kho sakko devanamindo bhagavantam gathaya ajjhabhasi: ","sn11.21:2.1":"“Kimsu chetva sukham seti, ","sn11.21:2.2":"kimsu chetva na socati; ","sn11.21:2.3":"Kissassu ekadhammassa, ","sn11.21:2.4":"vadham rocesi gotama”ti. ","sn11.21:3.1":"“Kodham chetva sukham seti, ","sn11.21:3.2":"kodham chetva na socati; ","sn11.21:3.3":"Kodhassa visamulassa, ","sn11.21:3.4":"madhuraggassa vasava; ","sn11.21:3.5":"Vadham ariya pasamsanti, ","sn11.21:3.6":"tanhi chetva na socati”ti. "}